      <title>纽约因数据泄露罚款 Geico 980 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/new-york-fines-geico-98-million-over-data-breach-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州总检察长办公室周一对汽车保险公司 Geico 处以 975 万美元罚款，原因是该公司实施黑客攻击，获取了该州 116,000 名司机的个人信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/new-york-fines-geico-98-million-over-data-breach-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 15:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
