      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-awards-special-retention-bonuses-hundreds-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻周一报道，花旗集团的财富部门今年已批准为数十名员工发放特殊留任奖金，以阻止更多银行家离职。]]></description>
